attributionInfo.brokerName: First Team Real Estate - Orange County

data.description: 3rd bedroom demising wall and closet to be completed by the seller prior to COE or a credit to the buyer to complete the work. Beautiful home on a large .47 acre parcel, with wonderful inside and outside living spaces. Quality upgrades from 2015 include fully remodeled kitchen, with new appliances, granite island & counters, all new cabinetry with soft close drawers & cupboard doors; remodeled bathrooms with granite and soft close cabinetry; french doors and a large new deck. Serene and expertly landscaped front & back courtyards, with mature citrus trees and perfect for entertaining. Fully paid solar system with minimal monthly electric costs. Note: This property has substantial extra space for adding an ADU and other outdoor amenities. Rental income from an ADU could be a huge financial perk. The storage shed conveys with the sale. This turn key home is close to so much that San Marcos has to offer.
